      <title>中国因饲料添加剂暂停美国 JBS 牛肉工厂的供货</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/china-halts-jbs-us-beef-plant-over-controversial-feed-additive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于在发往全球最大买家的肉类货物中发现了有争议的饲料添加剂，中国已禁止从 JBS SA 位于美国的一家大型牛肉工厂出口牛肉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/china-halts-jbs-us-beef-plant-over-controversial-feed-additive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
