      <title>由于代理成本飙升，Gildan 计划今年晚些时候首次发售债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/gildan-eyes-debut-bond-sale-later-this-year-as-proxy-costs-soar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位发言人向彭博新闻社透露，T 恤制造商 Gildan Activewear Inc. 计划最早在今年下半年发行债券，因为在一场昂贵的代理权争夺战之后，这家 T 恤制造商的杠杆率有所提高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/gildan-eyes-debut-bond-sale-later-this-year-as-proxy-costs-soar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:37:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
